   <p begin="00:17:02.897" end="00:17:04.899" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）うっ！　ギンガ団か…<br />（ピカチュウ）ピカ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:17:07.861" end="00:17:12.532" style="s1"><span style="s2">第３班 第５班はカンナギ<span style="s5"><span style="s6">遺跡</span><span style="s7">いせき</span></span>に急行！<br />現場一帯を<span style="s5"><span style="s6">封鎖</span><span style="s8">ふうさ</span></span>！</span></p> 
