   <p begin="00:19:22.370" end="00:19:24.622" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）ふざけるな<br />しらたまは<span style="s5"><span style="s6">渡</span><span style="s8">わた</span></span>さないぞ！</span></p> 
